description:
&quot;As a new arms dealer in the year 2025 you will bribe generals, build relationships, and trade over 300 real weapons. Hunted by 4 law enforcement agencies and compete with the top 10 arms dealers. You must find the best deals, rarest weapons and most useful vehicles to carry your goods.&quot;

v10 changelog:
-  Changed how resolutions work slightly.
-  Wars have been upgraded to be slightly more realistic and visually displayed.
-  Countries are more likely go to war with those closer to them while still having a lower chance for war with countries further away.
-  The Travel Challenges have been made easier.
-  Black Umbrella is now back.
-  Leaderboards are updating on Steam for Time Played and Most Wealth.

